properties.Name: Commission
properties.Description: A commission paid on the associated criteria as required. Commissions can be paid on the initial booking, renewal, or collection of payment as specified by the commission type.

Columns.Name: CommissionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Commission.

Columns.Name: CommissionBasisAmount
Columns.Description: The amount upon which the Commission is calculated.

Columns.Name: CommissionAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of the commission to be paid.

Columns.Name: SplitCommissionIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the commission was paid to two or more parties.

Columns.Name: CommissionEarnedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the commission is earned.

Columns.Name: CommissionDueDate
Columns.Description: The date that the commission is due to be paid.

Columns.Name: CommissionPaidDate
Columns.Description: The date that the commission is actually paid.

Columns.Name: CommissionNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the Commission.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionMinimumNumberUnits
Columns.Description: The minimum number of units for which the associated Commission Schedule is defined or valid.

Columns.Name: CommissionMaximumNumberUnits
Columns.Description: The maximum number of units for which the associated Commission Schedule is defined or valid.

Columns.Name: CommissionMinimumSalesRevenueAmount
Columns.Description: The minimum sales revenue amount for which the associated Commission Schedule is defined or valid.

Columns.Name: CommissionMaximumSalesRevenueAmount
Columns.Description: The maximum sales revenue amount for which the associated Commission Schedule is defined or valid.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleDetailStartDate
Columns.Description: The effective start date or first date that the Commission Schedule Detail is in effect.

Columns.Name: CommissionStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Commission Status.

Columns.Name: CommissionTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Commission Type.
